UBS sets call warrants on eight German stocks . UBS Securities GmbH has issued American - style call warrants of one million per tranche on shares of eight German stocks . The stocks are Adidas AG , BASF AG , Bayer AG , Daimler - Benz AG , Hoechst AG , Merck AG , SAP AG and Volkswagen AG . The maturity date for the warrants is June 15 , 2000 and the payment date is April 1 , 1997 . They are all listed on the Frankfurt and Duesseldorf exchanges and available in exercise lots of 100 . - - Reuter London Newsroom + 44 171 542 7658 
